{"tid":1170990,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國人法律界愛仲裁　容許走數 圍威喂 分贓 利益衝突　鄭若驊中","createTime":"2019-05-25T11:32:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-25T11:32:16.000Z","uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3e8f64b838ffa8c5b2a4504cca8b56d631689043","tid":1170990,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T11:32:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2427312400838170\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flynnleiwong%2Fposts%2F2427312400838170&d=QgRa2nBc7vcC6sJiZdE62NMQoCHxbgs64DeXVNsql00%3D&h=25bda659\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2427312400838170</a><br />\n<br />\n作者：黃鵹<br />\n<br />\n鄭若驊「走數、圍威喂、分贓、利益衝突」全部中晒<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2月6日：<br />\n<br />\n中國人嘅「法律界」80年代開始就好鍾意仲裁等等嘅ADR，容許走數、圍威喂、分贓、利益衝突。例如張舉能哈佛LLM dissertation就係「比較」走數。鄭若驊都係嗰行。"}]}